author: PlayStation
description:
STARSEEKER is a new game set within the Astroneer universe with a focus on discovery, cooperative expeditions, and camaraderie. Exploring deep space on the ESS Starseeker, players will need to work together with the entire crew of the space station to complete planet- wide objectives across a multitude of star systems using cutting edge technology.

The Street Fighter 6 Years 1-2 Fighters Edition will be available on June 5th!

This edition includes characters and stages released from Years 1 & 2 making a total of 26 characters, including their Outfit 1 Colors 3-10, and 20 stages. It's perfect for new players of all skill levels and interests looking to join the fight!

Check out the Wanderer: The Fragments of Fate launch trailer and get your time travelling shoes on.
